title: MisterMusic Show 379 - indie,alternative,rock radio
description:
MisterMusic Show #379 [2 hours] 192 kbps MP3 -


MisterMusic is back with new music this week from Half Moon Run, Deerhunter,
Go Go Berlin, and El Vy. Plus a pop hit from November 1981 is the "Oldie of the Week".
It's a blend of new indie and alternative music mixed with classic hits from 5 decades.

The MisterMusic Show is broadcast weekly and heard globally on RockXS internet radio.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

For recorded podcasts of the MisterMusic show, visit his podcast page-  
http://mistermusicshow.com/ . Shows are updated there first every Sunday.
Or you can google search mistermusicshow (spelled as one word) and you'll find it.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

MisterMusic is also a presenter on PodCloud1. The website that gives you shorter music segments and themes...easier 
to enjoy in the hectic schedules of today. Check it out- PodCloud1 'The One for Great Music' http://podcloud1.com/
